title: Urgent Care Walk in Clinics in San Francisco, Bay Area | GoHealth Urgent Care
description: Find urgent care near you in San Francisco, CA with Dignity Health-GoHealth Urgent Care for world-class care. Check-in online or walk-in for a visit today.
cleaned_text: We take great pride in keeping the communities we serve safe and cared for. And that's why we're proud to share that we've just administered what is likely the world's first vaccination for Respiratory Syncytial virus (RSV)! Daniel Kwan, medical director of Dignity Health-GoHealth Urgent Care, provided the vaccination today at our Cole Valley center in the Bay Area. We're proud to be part of a major milestone in protecting the communities we serve by administering what is likely the world's first vaccination for Respiratory Syncytial virus (RSV). *Beginning August 2023, the RSV vaccine will be available at Dignity Health-GoHealth Urgent Care in Cole Valley for adults aged 60 and older.
